name: Finch
description: '''Nils Wehowsky''' (born 13 April 1990), better known by his stage name '''Finch''', formerly '''Finch Asozial''' (stylized as '''FiNCH''' and '''FiNCH ASOZiAL'''), is a German rapper, [[Twitch (service)|Twitch]] [[Streamer (video gaming)|streamer]], [[YouTuber]] and [[battle rapper]].
